name: <3 Yummy Charm Necklace <3
description:
This is adorable!

I made this using linked chain.

To the chain i added yummy charms :-

*One Iced Donut

*2 Gingerbread Men

* 2 Strawberry Gaateaux Cake Slices

* 2 Ice Cream Cones

*2 Ice Lollies

Good Enough To Eat!

Looks really pretty on :-)

name: <3 Hello Kitty Bra and Knicker Set <3
description:
Sooo cute Hello Kitty bra and knickers!

For this i used all over hot pink Hello Kitty with hearts and kitty faces fabric :)

Elasticated ruffled bandeau style bra with bows.

Elasticated ruffle briefs with a hugggggge hot pink satin bow on the back!

Will fit a size S (8).

Purrrrfect for any Hello Kitty fan! <3
